# Optional personal overrides for one workstation.
# Copy to .env.local only for values that must differ on one workstation.
# NIDO runtime, Prisma, Vite and env-check load .env.local after .env in development.
# Keep shared required secrets in .env and only put machine-specific overrides here.

# Example:
# PORT=5001
# CLIENT_URLS="http://localhost:5173,http://127.0.0.1:5173"
